Package: diverging.bar
Type: Package
Title: Diverging Stacked Bar Charts for Likert Scale Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Ben", "Orwoll",
      email = "orwollb@ohsu.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides a function to create diverging stacked bar charts (Likert plots) for survey or questionnaire data with ordered categorical responses. The function centers the chart around a neutral midpoint, with negative responses on the left and positive responses on the right.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
